    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone looking for a reliable car without the brand-new price tag. It runs smoothly and looks great\u2014honestly, I'm sad to see it go! It's been a dependable companion and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 28900.0,
