    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, ensuring the structural and internal integrity of the chassis and drivetrain. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional tactile feedback and lateral grip. While the aesthetics reflect its status as a driven enthusiast vehicle, the suspension geometry remains tight, and the atmospheric induction note remains as sharp as ever. A true driver\u2019s specification for those who value mechanical pedigree over concours perfection.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean title. Minor exterior wear. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
