    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a well-cared-for 2018 executive sedan that strikes an excellent balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel rim\u2014standard signs of careful road use. The interior is finished in premium charcoal leather; the seats are firm and supportive, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s entry bolster. All electronic features, including the panoramic sunroof, navigation system, and heated seats, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in robust health. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a comprehensive file of maintenance records included. Recent work includes a fresh oil service, new cabin air filters, and a brake fluid flush. The tires have significant tread remaining, and the engine delivers smooth, consistent power without any hesitations. This is a dependable, honest vehicle that has been treated with respect by its previous owner.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
