      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's looking for a new home! This car has been such a reliable companion for me, perfect for everything from grocery runs to weekend getaways. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road with you right away. It drives like a dream and is super comfortable. Come give it a look\u2014I'm sure you'll fall in love with it just like I did!",
      "price": 32500.0,
