    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders and has undergone a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure timing precision. The power is sent to the rear wheels via a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis is robust, with the critical rear subframe reinforcement already completed. It sits on a revised suspension setup with fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers, preserving the original McPherson strut/multi-link geometry. Recent maintenance includes a valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system refresh with a high-flow water pump. This is a driver-spec example that balances raw performance with proven mechanical reliability.",
